data.description: Virtually everything has been remodeled or replaced by the previous owner between 2020-2022. Current owner added a high-end Pure Life water filtration and purification system. Wait until you see the beautiful features of this home from the exposed beams, fabulous kitchen with gorgeous granite top island, built-in wine chiller, gas cooktop stove and sliding barn doors on pantry to the oversized deck leading you to the impressive outdoor living area complete with stone grill, bench and fire pit on the large fenced and flat yard offering privacy and enjoyment. Be sure turn on the ceiling fans which are also BlueTooth accessible. Exterior building is insulated and has electricity and window AC for your own home office/business or storage. Custom built chicken coop could also make a great kennel or protected garden area. Only a few minutes to Winthrop University and shopping/dining areas in a growing area.
